statements: SELECT * FROM neural_network_changes ORDER BY change_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT network_name, architecture FROM neural_network_changes WHERE change_id IN (1, 3, 5)
SELECT * FROM neural_network_changes WHERE network_name = 'ExampleNetwork'
SELECT change_id, network_name, change_timestamp FROM neural_network_changes ORDER BY change_id ASC
SELECT network_name, COUNT(*) AS count FROM neural_network_changes GROUP BY network_name HAVING count > 1
SELECT * FROM neural_network_changes ORDER BY network_name DESC;
SELECT network_name, architecture FROM neural_network_changes WHERE change_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT change_id, network_name, hyperparameters->>'learning_rate' AS learning_rate FROM neural_network_changes WHERE architecture ILIKE '%CNN%';
SELECT AVG(change_id) AS avg_change_id, COUNT(*) AS total_changes FROM neural_network_changes GROUP BY network_name;
SELECT change_id, network_name, CAST(change_timestamp AS DATE) AS change_date FROM neural_network_changes WHERE hyperparameters->>'optimizer' = 'Adam' ORDER BY change_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures;
SELECT architecture_name, last_updated FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM architecture_changes ORDER BY change_date DESC;
SELECT architecture_name, hyperparameters->'batch_size' AS batch_size FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 2;
SELECT architecture_name, change_description FROM neural_network_architectures JOIN architecture_changes ON neural_network_architectures.id = architecture_changes.architecture_id;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures ORDER BY architecture_name DESC;
SELECT architecture_name, last_updated FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 1;
SELECT architecture_name, hyperparameters FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE last_updated > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY last_updated DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_changes FROM architecture_changes WHERE change_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01';

SELECT architecture_name, change_description FROM neural_network_architectures JOIN architecture_changes ON neural_network_architectures.id = architecture_changes.architecture_id ORDER BY change_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures;
SELECT id, architecture_name FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 1;
SELECT architecture_name, hyperparameters->>'learning_rate' AS learning_rate FROM neural_network_architectures;
SELECT * FROM architecture_changes ORDER BY change_date DESC;
SELECT version_number, change_description FROM version_control WHERE architecture_id = 2 ORDER BY version_number;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures ORDER BY architecture_name DESC;
SELECT id, architecture_name FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id < 100 AND architecture_name ILIKE 'ResNet%' ORDER BY id ASC;

SELECT nn.id, nn.architecture_name, vc.version_number FROM neural_network_architectures nn JOIN version_control vc ON nn.id = vc.architecture_id WHERE vc.version_number > 2.0 ORDER BY nn.id ASC, vc.version_number DESC;

SELECT ac.change_description, ac.change_date, nn.architecture_name FROM architecture_changes ac JOIN neural_network_architectures nn ON ac.architecture_id = nn.id WHERE ac.change_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01' ORDER BY ac.change_date DESC;

SELECT nn.id, nn.architecture_name, ac.change_description FROM neural_network_architectures nn LEFT JOIN architecture_changes ac ON nn.id = ac.architecture_id WHERE ac.change_description IS NOT NULL ORDER BY nn.id ASC, ac.change_description ASC;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures;
SELECT architecture_name, architecture_details FROM neural_network_architectures ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM hyperparameters WHERE architecture_id = 1;
SELECT change_description, changed_at FROM changes_tracking WHERE architecture_id = 2 ORDER BY changed_at ASC;
SELECT version_number, commit_message, committed_at FROM version_control WHERE architecture_id = 3 ORDER BY committed_at DESC;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures;
SELECT architecture_name, created_at FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 5;
SELECT architecture_name, COUNT(id) AS total_architectures FROM neural_network_architectures GROUP BY architecture_name;
SELECT c.id, c.change_description, v.commit_message FROM changes_tracking c JOIN version_control v ON c.architecture_id = v.architecture_id;
SELECT id, architecture_name, architecture_details, created_at FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE architecture_name LIKE 'CNN%' ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures;
SELECT architecture_name, modifications FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM architecture_changes ORDER BY change_date DESC;
SELECT hyperparameters->'learning_rate' AS learning_rate FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 2;
SELECT version_id, version_description FROM architecture_versions WHERE architecture_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM neural_network_architectures;
SELECT architecture_name, hyperparameters FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM model_training_logs ORDER BY training_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT architecture_name, modifications FROM neural_network_architectures WHERE architecture_name LIKE '%Convolutional%';
SELECT architecture_id, change_description, change_date FROM architecture_changes WHERE architecture_id = 2 ORDER BY change_date ASC;
